---
import CvtLayout from "../../../layouts/CvtLayout.astro";
---

<CvtLayout title="Architecture — CVT">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-white">Architecture</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-slate-300">CVT separates immutable facts from versioned interpretation. Registry events flow into <code class="rounded bg-white/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-teal-200">trust_events</code>; the policy engine produces snapshots and passport views filtered by partner tier and consent.</p>

    <ul class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-slate-400">
      <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Event model</strong> — append-only facts; reversals add compensating events</li>
      <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Policy engine</strong> — versioned trust levels, good standing, dormancy</li>
      <li><strong class="text-slate-200">APIs</strong> — public passport, partner Soft / Enhanced / Hard search</li>
      <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Database</strong> — Supabase Postgres; riders registry + trust tables</li>
    </ul>

    <a href="/cvt/docs/trust-architecture-v1" class="mt-10 inline-block rounded-full bg-teal-600 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-teal-500">Read Trust Architecture v1</a>
  </div>
</CvtLayout>

<style>.font-display { font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif; }</style>
